# =============================================================================
# Trivy Ignore List — Known False Positives / Accepted Risks
# =============================================================================
# Add CVE IDs here to suppress known vulnerabilities that are:
#   1. False positives (not applicable to our usage)
#   2. Accepted risks (reviewed and documented)
#   3. Awaiting upstream fixes (temporarily suppressed)
#
# Format: one CVE ID per line
# Example: CVE-2023-12345
#
# IMPORTANT: Every entry MUST have a comment explaining WHY it's ignored.
# Review this file quarterly and remove entries that have been patched.
# =============================================================================
